---

<section class="personas" id="personas">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Built for How You Work</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Whether you're accelerating your career, protecting your org, or living in the terminal - Caro adapts to you.
    </p>

    <div class="personas-grid">
      <!-- The Accelerator -->
      <div class="persona-card accelerator" data-persona="accelerator">
        <div class="persona-icon">
          <span>üöÄ</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="persona-title">The Accelerator</h3>
        <p class="persona-role">Individual Developer</p>

        <div class="persona-problem">
          <span class="label problem">The Friction</span>
          <p>You're smart. But memorizing 500 flags and options for tools you use twice a month? That's not intelligence, it's trivia.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-solution">
          <span class="label solution">The Unlock</span>
          <p>Express intent in English. Get validated, runnable commands. Ship faster without the Stack Overflow detour.</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="persona-benefits">
          <li>10x faster command discovery</li>
          <li>Learn shell idioms naturally</li>
          <li>Build career-defining skills</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="persona-expanded" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="expanded-content">
            <h4>How Accelerators Use Caro</h4>
            <div class="use-case">
              <code class="input">"find all Python files changed in the last week"</code>
              <code class="output">find . -name "*.py" -mtime -7</code>
            </div>
            <p class="expanded-note">Caro teaches you the underlying command syntax as you use it, building real terminal expertise over time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="persona-cta" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="cta-text">See how it works</span>
          <span class="cta-icon">‚Üí</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- The Guardian -->
      <div class="persona-card guardian" data-persona="guardian">
        <div class="persona-icon">
          <span>üõ°Ô∏è</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="persona-title">The Guardian</h3>
        <p class="persona-role">Security & Platform Lead</p>

        <div class="persona-problem">
          <span class="label problem">The Risk</span>
          <p>Every AI tool your team uses is a potential data leak. Cloud APIs see your infrastructure. Your secrets. Your blind spots.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-solution">
          <span class="label solution">The Shield</span>
          <p>100% local execution. Zero data collection. Pre-execution validation catches dangerous commands before they run.</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="persona-benefits">
          <li>Air-gapped friendly</li>
          <li>52+ dangerous patterns blocked</li>
          <li>Full audit capability</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="persona-expanded" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="expanded-content">
            <h4>What Caro Catches</h4>
            <div class="use-case danger">
              <code class="input blocked">rm -rf /</code>
              <span class="blocked-badge">‚õî BLOCKED</span>
            </div>
            <div class="use-case danger">
              <code class="input blocked">:()&#123; :|:& &#125;;:</code>
              <span class="blocked-badge">‚õî FORK BOMB</span>
            </div>
            <p class="expanded-note">52+ dangerous patterns are validated before any command runs. Your team is protected by default.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="persona-cta" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="cta-text">See what's blocked</span>
          <span class="cta-icon">‚Üí</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- The Operator -->
      <div class="persona-card operator" data-persona="operator">
        <div class="persona-icon">
          <span>‚ö°</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="persona-title">The Operator</h3>
        <p class="persona-role">SRE / DevOps Engineer</p>

        <div class="persona-problem">
          <span class="label problem">The Chaos</span>
          <p>Production is down. You're SSH'd into a box you've never seen. Is it BSD? Linux? What's the find syntax here again?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="persona-solution">
          <span class="label solution">The Edge</span>
          <p>Platform-aware commands. macOS vs Linux vs BSD - Caro knows the difference. You focus on the problem, not the syntax.</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="persona-benefits">
          <li>Cross-platform intelligence</li>
          <li>Instant command generation</li>
          <li>Works in any terminal</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="persona-expanded" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="expanded-content">
            <h4>Platform Intelligence</h4>
            <div class="platform-grid">
              <div class="platform-item">
                <span class="platform-name">macOS</span>
                <code>find . -name "*.log" -mtime +7</code>
              </div>
              <div class="platform-item">
                <span class="platform-name">Linux</span>
                <code>find . -name "*.log" -mtime +7</code>
              </div>
              <div class="platform-item">
                <span class="platform-name">BSD</span>
                <code>find . -name "*.log" -mtime +7d</code>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="expanded-note">Same intent, platform-correct syntax. Caro detects your OS and adjusts automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="persona-cta" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="cta-text">See platform support</span>
          <span class="cta-icon">‚Üí</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { track } from '@vercel/analytics';

  document.querySelectorAll('.persona-cta').forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const card = button.closest('.persona-card') as HTMLElement;
      const expanded = card?.querySelector('.persona-expanded');
      const isExpanded = button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
      const persona = card?.dataset.persona || 'unknown';

      // Track persona engagement
      if (!isExpanded) {
        track('persona_expand', { persona });
      }

      // Toggle state
      button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', (!isExpanded).toString());
      expanded?.setAttribute('aria-hidden', isExpanded.toString());
      card?.classList.toggle('is-expanded', !isExpanded);

      // Update button text
      const ctaText = button.querySelector('.cta-text') as HTMLElement;
      if (ctaText) {
        ctaText.textContent = isExpanded ? (button as HTMLElement).dataset.originalText || 'See how it works' : 'Close';
        if (!(button as HTMLElement).dataset.originalText) {
          (button as HTMLElement).dataset.originalText = ctaText.textContent || '';
        }
      }
    });
  });

  // Track scroll to personas section
  const personasSection = document.getElementById('personas');
  let hasTrackedPersonasView = false;

  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting && !hasTrackedPersonasView) {
        track('section_view', { section: 'personas' });
        hasTrackedPersonasView = true;
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.3 });

  if (personasSection) {
    observer.observe(personasSection);
  }
</script>

<style>
  .personas {
    padding: 100px 20px;
    background: #0f0f14;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #888;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .personas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .persona-card {
    background: #16161f;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .persona-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .persona-card.accelerator::before {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b35, #ff8c42);
  }

  .persona-card.guardian::before {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #50fa7b, #69ff94);
  }

  .persona-card.operator::before {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8be9fd, #a4ffff);
  }

  .persona-card:hover {
    border-color: #333;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .persona-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .persona-card.is-expanded {
    border-color: #ff6b35;
  }

  .persona-card.is-expanded::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .persona-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: #1f1f2a;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .persona-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .persona-role {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .persona-problem, .persona-solution {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .label.problem {
    background: rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.15);
    color: #ff5555;
  }

  .label.solution {
    background: rgba(80, 250, 123, 0.15);
    color: #50fa7b;
  }

  .persona-problem p, .persona-solution p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .persona-benefits {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #222;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .persona-benefits li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #888;
    padding: 8px 0;
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .persona-benefits li::before {
    content: '‚úì';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #ff6b35;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* Expanded section */
  .persona-expanded {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .persona-expanded[aria-hidden="false"] {
    max-height: 400px;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .expanded-content {
    background: #0a0a0f;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #1e1e24;
  }

  .expanded-content h4 {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .use-case {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .use-case.danger {
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .use-case code {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: block;
  }

  .use-case code.input {
    background: #1e1e24;
    color: #888;
  }

  .use-case code.output {
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
    color: #22c55e;
  }

  .use-case code.blocked {
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    color: #ef4444;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .blocked-badge {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ef4444;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .platform-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .platform-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .platform-name {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #888;
    min-width: 60px;
  }

  .platform-item code {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #22c55e;
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .expanded-note {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
  }

  /* CTA Button */
  .persona-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ff6b35;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid #ff6b35;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .persona-cta:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1);
  }

  .persona-cta[aria-expanded="true"] {
    background: #ff6b35;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .cta-icon {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .persona-cta[aria-expanded="true"] .cta-icon {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .personas-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .personas {
      padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .persona-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .use-case.danger {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
